  2. ART ASSETS. Sprite art, portraits, altar/vision imagery, and music
     referenced by this project are NOT included in this repository and are
     NOT licensed here. Each asset retains the rights of its respective
     creator. Users supply their own art (see README).

  3. NO DERIVATIVES POLICY. The author has chosen the ND (NoDerivatives)
     component deliberately: this project represents the author's preferred
     "official-pairing" vision of the characters. Modifying, forking-and-
